                <h1>Snoop Dogg: The Iconic Rap Legend</h1>
                <p>Snoop Dogg, born Calvin Cordozar Broadus Jr., is an iconic rapper, songwriter, and actor known for his laid-back style and distinctive voice. Rising to fame in the early '90s, Snoop has sold millions of albums and collaborated with many artists. His influence extends beyond music into cannabis culture and philanthropy.</p>
